quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  26,176,N’abantu bo mukibira nabone barahakanye intumwa z’Imana
  26,177,"Mugihe intumwa y’Imana Shuebu (iii) yababwira ati:- mbega mwebwe ntimutinya Imana yanyu"
  26,178,Mu vy’ukuri jewe kuri mwebwe nd’intumwa y’Imana yizigiwe
  26,179,Nimutinye Imana yanyu kandi mu ngamburukire
  26,180,"Kandi sindabasaba impembo iyariyo yose, mugabo impembo yanje iri kumuremyi w’ibiremwa vyose"
  26,181,Nimwuzuze igipimo neza mugabo ntimube mubantu bagabanya kuri ivyo bipimo
  26,182,Kandi mupime kuminzani y’ukuri
  26,183,"Kandi ntimuba gabanirize abantu kubintu vyabo, kandi ntimugendere kuri iy’Isi namwe muri mu bantu b’abononyi"
  26,184,Nimutinye uwabaremye hamwe n’ibiremwa vyabayeho vyose
  26,185,"Nabo bavuga bati:- mu vy’ukuri wewe uri mubantu barozwe"
  26,186,"Na wewe ntiwari bwabeho, mugabo uri mubantu nkatwe, mu vy’ukuri twebwe tukubona nkuko uri mu bantu b’ababeshi"
  26,187,"Rero\tnutumanurire\tibimanyu\tvy’amajuru\tniwaba\turi\tmubantu bavugisha ukuri"
  26,188,"Nawe abishura ati:- Umuremyi wanje niwe afise ubumenyi buhagije bw’ivyo muriko muragira"
  26,189,"Baramwihakanye baca bahura n’ibihano vy’umusi w’igitutu, ntankeka ivo vyari ibihano vy’umusi uhambaye"
  26,190,Mu vy’ukuri muri ibi vyose harimwo ibitekerezo mugabo benshi muribo ntibari mubantu bemera Imana yabo y’ukuri
  26,191,"Mu\tvy’ukuri\tUmuremyi\twawe\tniwe\tnyene\tububasha\tn’impuhwe zihagije"